snippet.title: PlayStation - Click Manga - Dynamic Robot Taisen 2 - Kyoufu! Akuma Zoku Fukkatsu (1999)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Click Manga: Dynamic Robot Taisen 2: Kyoufu! Akuma Zoku Fukkatsu is an Action game, published by Tokuma Shoten, which was released in Japan in 1999.
